&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Content Marketing Strategies<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-40833af elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"40833af\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>HubSpot gives inbound marketing a competitive edge through content marketing, one of the most powerful tools. Content marketing is a marketing strategy focused on creating and distributing valuable, relevant content to attract, retain, and clearly define an audience \u2014 and, ultimately, drive consumer behavior a valuable Consumers find the helpful content, ideally to answer their questions or solve problems with solutions.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bb2701e elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"bb2701e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Creating Value with Content<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-02992b6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"02992b6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul><li><b>Identify Audience Needs: <\/b>Review the data from your buyer personas to see what information your audience seeks.<\/li><li><b>Develop Relevant Content:<\/b> Produce blog posts, videos, ebooks, and infographics that offer your audience advice or exciting information.<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ad5300d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ad5300d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">HubSpot\u2019s Content Creation Tools<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6d17c9f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6d17c9f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul><li><b>SEO Recommendations: <\/b>HubSpot suggests keywords to help your content rank higher in search results.<\/li><li><b>Content Management System:<\/b> Easily manage and publish content that captures leads.<\/li><\/ul><p>When you deliver helpful content regularly, targeting your prospects&#8217; interests and needs, you draw more eyes to your brand, who tend to view you as an expert in their topic of choice. That trust stands between a visitor and making them into a lead, then turning that lead into the customer.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-58eaace all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"58eaace\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-6\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Utilizing Email Marketing to Nurture Leads<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4a40a3f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"4a40a3f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Email marketing is still a very effective strategy for nurturing leads into customers. Businesses use HubSpot to tailor email campaigns that serve the most need-to-know and when you need content immediately.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1df6d70 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"1df6d70\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Email-Marketing-to-Nurture-Leads-1-1024x576.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-16782\" alt=\"Email Marketing to Nurture Leads\" srcset=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Email-Marketing-to-Nurture-Leads-1-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Email-Marketing-to-Nurture-Leads-1-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Email-Marketing-to-Nurture-Leads-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Email-Marketing-to-Nurture-Leads-1.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e072ae3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e072ae3\" data-element_t